subject: Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Nascar celebrates the end of every season with lunches, dinners and photo opportunities in Manhattan, and the showpiece has become what Nascar calls a Victory Lap in Midtown.
